12.31	The_Fly_(George_Langelaan)	The Fly (George Langelaan)	"The Fly" is a short story by George Langelaan that was published in the June, 1957 issue of Playboy magazine. It was first filmed in 1958, and then again in 1986. An opera of the same name by Howard Shore premiered at the Théâtre du Châtelet, Paris, in 2008.	
